 LAUNCHING Transport Month, minister Fikile Mbalula got the
chance to experience the flames of taxi maths. Mbalula is in Tshwane launching Transport Month and
showcasing the mechanisms that promote the availability and interestedness of
public transport for persons with disabilities. He said Mzansi has invested millions on the Bus Rapid Transport
in most of the metros. “They add on and assist in getting our people to work,
schools and higher institutions of learning,” Mbalua said. 